      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and honestly runs like a dream\u2014perfect for getting around town or heading out on a spontaneous road trip! I've made sure to keep up with the maintenance, so it's all ready for its next big adventure. I'd love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
