      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous manifold pressure response. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and reinforced rear subframe mounting points to maintain torsional rigidity. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein dampers and polyurethane bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry remains dialed for spirited cornering. While the exterior displays minor road-wear patina, the mechanical synchronization and thermal management are excellent, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
